        at org.apache.storm.shade.org.apache.zookeeper.ClientCnxn$EventThread.processEvent(ClientCnxn.java:533) [storm-shaded-deps-2.1.0.jar:2.1.1-SNAPSHOT]
        at org.apache.storm.shade.org.apache.zookeeper.ClientCnxn$EventThread.run(ClientCnxn.java:508) [storm-shaded-deps-2.1.0.jar:2.1.1-SNAPSHOT]&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This appears to be a regression from the migration from clojure to java in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-1267&quot; title=&quot;port backtype.storm.command.set-log-level to java&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;STORM-1267&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;STORM-1267&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
